This is my own version of the 3D-printed SNL logo.  By the phrase &quot;my own version,&quot; what I actually mean to say is, &quot;I could not find the appropriate font, so here you go.&quot;
Please enjoy back-lighting this object with results similar to SNL's.  I quadruple dare you, fancy printer people!
:D

This thing is a remix of the linked E3D mount for the K8200. 
Since I occasionally change the nozzle depending on what printing resolution and speed I need, I needed a way to easily detach the airduct/fan. This is what my mind came up with. 
//edit: the airduct is the one from the original <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:267337" >http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:267337</a>.
